---
const heroTitleChars = [..."Be a Good Coiner"];
---

<section class="overflow-hidden bg-[var(--bg-canvas)] pb-0 text-center">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1094px] px-5 pt-[74px] md:pt-[67px]">
    <p class="hero-kicker mb-6 text-center text-[26px] font-bold leading-[39px] tracking-[0.04em] text-[var(--text-primary)]">
      トレードを、感覚から仕組みへ。
    </p>

    <h1
      class="mx-auto mb-6 text-center text-[clamp(60px,7.71vw,111px)] leading-[1] tracking-[-0.055em] text-[var(--text-primary)] md:text-[111px] md:leading-[111px]"
      style="font-family: 'Avenir Next', 'Avenir', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif; font-weight: 900; font-kerning: normal;"
    >
      <span class="hero-title" aria-label="Be a Good Coiner">
        {heroTitleChars.map((char, index) => (
          <span
            class="hero-title-char"
            style={`animation-delay: ${180 + index * 55}ms;`}
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            {char === " " ? "\u00A0" : char}
          </span>
        ))}
      </span>
    </h1>

    <p
      class="mx-auto max-w-[760px] text-center text-[18px] font-medium leading-[36px] tracking-[0.04em] text-[var(--text-secondary)]"
      style="font-family: 'Inter', 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;"
    >
      グッドコイナーは、感覚や感情に左右されず、<br />
      明確なルールと目的に基づいて暗号資産を売買するトレード管理アプリです。<br />
      「Be a Good Coiner」を合言葉に、再現性のあるトレードを優しくサポートします。
    </p>

    <div class="mx-auto mt-9 flex w-80 flex-col items-center gap-5">
      <a
        id="download"
        href="#"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2.5 rounded-[var(--radius-pill)] bg-[var(--accent-yellow)] px-8 py-4 text-[18px] font-bold leading-[32.38px] tracking-[0.01em] text-[var(--text-primary)] transition hover:bg-[var(--accent-yellow-hover)]"
      >
        <img
          src="/assets/icons/Finder_Icon_macOS.png"
          alt=""
          aria-hidden="true"
          class="h-7 w-7"
        />
        Mac版をダウンロード
      </a>
      <p class="whitespace-nowrap text-center text-[12px] font-normal leading-[12px] tracking-[0.04em] text-[var(--text-tertiary)]">
        ※現在GMOコインユーザーのみ利用可能。順次拡張予定です。
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mx-auto mt-14 max-w-[1320px] px-4 md:px-6">
    <div class="relative pb-[14px]">
      <div class="absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 top-[14px] rounded-[var(--radius-panel)] border-[11px] border-[var(--border-soft)] bg-[#d4d4d8]"></div>
      <div class="relative rounded-[var(--radius-panel)] border-[11px] border-[var(--border-soft)] bg-[var(--bg-product-surface)] shadow-[var(--shadow-panel)]">
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-[37px] bg-[var(--bg-product-surface)]">
          <video
            src="/dashboard.mp4"
            autoplay
            muted
            loop
            playsinline
            class="block h-auto w-full"
          ></video>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-kicker {
    display: inline-block;
    white-space: nowrap;
    animation: hero-kicker-reveal 0.48s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.2, 1) 0.05s both;
    transform-origin: left center;
  }

  .hero-title {
    display: inline-flex;
    flex-wrap: nowrap;
  }

  .hero-title-char {
    display: inline-block;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(18px) scaleY(0.92) rotate(-4deg);
    animation: hero-char-wave 0.62s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.75, 0.2, 1) both;
    will-change: transform, opacity;
  }

  @keyframes hero-kicker-reveal {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateX(-28px);
      clip-path: inset(0 100% 0 0);
    }

    100% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateX(0);
      clip-path: inset(0 0 0 0);
    }
  }

  @keyframes hero-char-wave {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(18px) scaleY(0.92) rotate(-4deg);
    }

    55% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(-10px) scaleY(1.04) rotate(1deg);
    }

    100% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0) scaleY(1) rotate(0deg);
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .hero-kicker,
    .hero-title-char {
      animation: none;
      opacity: 1;
      transform: none;
    }
  }
</style>
